 A female suicide bomber in Buni Yadi, Yobe State, in the early hours of Friday, killed herself and injured three others when a bomb strapped round her waist exploded. An eye witness who declined to be identified told the News Agency of Nigeria that the incident occurred at about dawn prayer time at Fulatari ward in Buni Yadi. The news agencyÂ gathered that the injured persons had been taken to hospital and were in stable condition.